{"hee3877f3g5f4cg461ag8d45gb01a4625eced": ["C'mon Alfie, make it <i>spicy.</i>", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "977965af-a125-dc77-b392-830623abb4bd"], "had48b82bgf48dg4f8bgaf1cg9dcd84f3bd8a": ["All right, erm, 'hearts aquiver, we raised our bows...'", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "848bb221-3b66-3ce3-a9df-0c57a4ee100b"], "h944651f0g89bcg4932ga9e9g7282e50432d2": ["Pfft, none of that poetic stuff! Something like...", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "4a7eb6d0-99e4-35bc-9996-74b024914187"], "h04edbd46gabefg4757g850fgd4a602fffdc2": ["'Goblins swarmed, but we were brave and fried them all with a Thunder Wave!'", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "fc07dab9-39b8-8b32-80d9-616a41512116"], "hd3042803gd282g47b1g82dfgbac4474bef2f": ["But that's not what happened...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "23dcf175-a634-29bc-00d2-72e555f83be5"], "hf340d2f8g3839g4a96ga910g185e833709d6": ["Live a little!", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "200467c5-efab-9260-d9ed-0b6a749561e8"], "h8f83a60dg7f8bg4082ga930gaa1dc2c5d9b3": ["How about... 'two tiefling queens, frightful and fierce.'", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "0dab2e78-fecc-0ce1-369f-cd9cfff867fb"], "hef06b5e4gb460g4d6ag9bffg8d5b399a079d": ["That's more like it! How many goblins did we kill? Ten?", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "2c001b30-c9f7-b9cb-f831-ffffae1e7dd2"], "h216a7bdfgf1eeg4600gb1e1g949d30a72641": ["Let's make it twenty.", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "512a815d-8a3d-41dd-7381-b7dda037e2ac"], "he0a86c25gc81ag4665g8217g5d8c6c6ce697": ["Haha! That's my girl!", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "5a048e80-a94f-2f86-5bf7-0042219f3b1a"], "hff6cf3f8gf4e3g44e8g8b5bg47767acbbe49": ["What are you going to do in the city?", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "4aa06444-2d35-0422-6d1c-926ea3683d82"], "h1e9f89e9g46d1g4f85g9871g75deff368b28": ["Eh, there's always work for a guard. You?", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "f11f2c93-978c-d59c-ec62-c9c81b187c0b"], "hffcd9932g6882g495fg9b4eg2221643b7f27": ["I've always wanted to sing at the Elfsong Tavern.", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "f1cb71ad-b62d-3d9b-e760-7c6a51117b41"], "h5c17bd1ag5d59g4652g8df8g54201fc90d3d": ["If the owner has any sense, they'll hire you on the spot.", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "45635e23-c471-dbba-3bf3-4b3f6cfa8797"], "h49f7d011g9bc3g4171g8fc2gdcbbd631bfaa": ["What's your plan for the city?", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "b7424d67-690e-7678-e43f-d7b270e69797"], "h7ad45d52g717eg4f16g9ebdg46f77d559da3": ["I don't know, anymore.", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "d93b7aed-815a-3723-359e-aa1e7a57d9dc"], "h79c3af92gb07bg444dg9b0agee9490376341": ["Don't worry. I can get us both jobs as guards. If you practice. ", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "55f30e79-b687-864d-a251-f6f88719e569"], "h49cd9c20ged35g4727gb311g1046b2a3e499": ["Lesson number one: intimidation. Go.", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "d4c32c2e-a267-4960-1bb9-9bc3789d5f22"], "h952ffc38gc92dg4546g957bg2c2dca3321af": ["All right. *ahem* What - what you looking at?", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "8ddc4333-3f49-1ef6-d981-d3db00363153"], "h722a0b08g9eccg4cf4gb250gb28fd10d69bb": ["Aha! Only a child would find that intimidating. ", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "423fdee7-10fd-258b-90a2-5a976015b143"], "h362a04b1gbe59g40d7g93f9g1c223685a1b2": ["This is a bad idea. ", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "1be12dfc-f74a-e685-9a47-3f95e30a03ac"], "hede1d7begdef4g4ed4ga500g4f4ef30e0bb1": ["Hey, don't talk like that. We'll work on it.", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "1b7c86b3-8e0d-c063-2572-da5b419c98e4"], "h1ffee719g073fg48bbgbad1g581e8cbdee8a": ["You got friends or family in the city?", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "25dec1de-e9b7-d21f-260e-2fa74c03595e"], "h2bfc850fga4f6g41a8g838bga42f16074f35": ["None. You?", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "ae66b493-645e-668c-76b4-a99c80c32d9f"], "hef156cc5g36a6g45fegadddgc625ac94dcd0": ["A sister. She's got two boys - the sweetest things you've ever seen.", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "f0440843-a611-ef81-a700-6acc659b843f"], "h5147a79ag4dd7g4627g86f6g64ab57eb892a": ["I can introduce you all, if you want?", "23129d6c-8d39-4a4c-a4f6-cfc6637b597c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "0773ba23-df67-4d94-9dda-6fbadea3f397"], "h42cfb1beg5841g4747gafb2gd96041a51c1f": ["I'd like that. ", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_Bard_Flirty.html", "946856ac-8069-2a5c-a5ce-7c960384a2cd"]}